rows.label: qev014304_MSG0001
rows.name:
Cheche was the Nopon informant who told us about
Alex's plans to kill all the xenoforms in New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0002
rows.name: He's GOT to know where they're hiding![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0003
rows.name:
So hurry on over to the west end of Melville Street and
hear what he has to say![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0004
rows.name: You've got to hurry and stop Alex![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0005
rows.name:
I don't like violence any more than Eliza,
but we can't let more xenoforms be killed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0006
rows.name:
New LA can't move towards peace and equality until
Alex and his plans have been stopped.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0007
rows.name:
Welcome back! I guess we won't have to worry about
Alex again, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0008
rows.name: Eliza's dying to hear your report.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014304_MSG0009
rows.name: Go tell her all about it, [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]
